      • findGameById

        public Game findGameById(int gameId,
                         User user)
                  throws ServiceException
        The method returns the game. If the user role is USER the method returns the game only if it contains all types of bets for participants. If the user is null or its role is not USER, it will return the game in any case.

      • isGameDeleted

        public boolean isGameDeleted(int gameId)
                      throws ServiceException
        The method delete the game. Delete bets on the game from users and returns them money in the method BetService.isGameBetsDeletedByGameId(int) (bets table), delete the types of bets on game participants in the method GameBetsDao.deleteAllByGameId(int) (game_bets table), delete participants for the game in the method GameHorsesDao.deleteAll(Integer) (game_horses table), delete the game (games table).
        Parameters:
        gameId -
        Returns:
        true, if the game is deleted
        Throws:
        ServiceException
        See Also:
        BetService.isGameBetsDeletedByGameId(int), GameBetsDao.deleteAllByGameId(int), GameHorsesDao.deleteAll(Integer)
